title: Population of the Netherlands 2019 , by age
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of inhabitants, with a total of 5 data points. The chart has 2 significant trends.
The longest trend is extremely negative which exists from 0_-_20_years to 40_-_65_years.
But, the next significant trend is slightly positive which exists from 40_-_65_years to 80_years_and_older.
gold: This statistic shows the population of the Netherlands in 2019 , by age . On January 1 , 2019 there were approximately 3.8 million people younger than 20 years living in the Netherlands . The largest age group was formed by those between 40 and 65 years old .
